text:
Amana-chan, Tenka-chan, we just got
some doughnuts while we were out.

Want to have some together?
And if you'd like, Producer-san can join us too.

Then Amana,
will get some drinks ready!
Doughnuts are the best, aren't they?
I'll send a thank you email.

You know, when there are different types
inside the box... It's fun to choose, isn't it?

Hehe, this excitement...
Producer understands it too, right?

The drinks will be ready soon,
so sit tight!

Thank you...
I'll give you my business card later.

But for now...
Let's enjoy our doughnut time slowly.
